spdfcore

Class Id

  • java.lang.Object
    • spdfcore.Id
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Actor, Modifier, Port

    public class Id
extends java.lang.Object
    Identifies a named entity: actor or port. It can be used as a map key. It contains three constant fields: <1> function (actor type, e.g "Idct") <2> name (actor/port name, e.g. "idct", "in" ) <3> graph.
